parameters:
"There it is!! The ore on that monster's back is the
material we need!!"
"Be careful, it's a really strong monster."

"I can definitely sense a different aura from it. This is
truly a formidable foe, Suelle."
"I know!! I'll take shelter until it's over!!"
"You were quite strong... But I was just too powerful."
"Now, this is what we were after, right?"

"   Analyzing specific frequencies to improve energy
efficiency... Converting the usual spell formula into a
special barrier..."
"Ah- yes yes, let's save that talk for when we get back."

"Yeah... I'm just nervous about whether what I've made will
actually work, so I keep checking it over and over..."
"Don't worry. I believe in your abilities."

"Well, if you've kept me waiting this long only to fail,
you'll be in for a special punishment course, you know?"

"Oh, that's scary... I'll put my spirit into making it
work!!"

"Just moderately, okay?... I'll also do my best to look for
clues."
Rise: "Alright, let's give it our all!!"
Meanwhile, in a certain underground facility...
